msgid "Remuneration"
msgstr "Винагорода"

#: .uk.SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_DESC
msgid ""
"A <style=cIsUtility>choice</style> between three <style=cIsHealth>powerful "
"items</style> appears closeby at the <style=cIsUtility>start of each stage</"
"style>."
msgstr ""
"Поруч з'являється <style=cIsUtility>вибір</style> між трьома "
"<style=cIsHealth>потужними предметами</style> <style=cIsUtility>на початку "
"кожного етапу</style>."

#: .uk.SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_PICKUP
msgid "<link=\"textWavy\">... At what cost?...</link>"
msgstr "<link=\"textWavy\">... Якою ціною?...</link>"

#: .uk.SS2_REMUNERATION_TERMINAL_NAME
msgid "Pedestal"
msgstr "П'єдестал"

#: .uk.SS2_REMUNERATION_TERMINAL_CONTEXT
msgid "<link=\"textWavy\">Complete transaction</link>"
msgstr "<link=\"textWavy\">Завершити транзакцію</link>"

#: .uk.SS2_ITEM_REMUNERATION_LORE
msgid ""
"<link=\"textShaky\">What is your legacy?</link>\n"
"\n"
"Nothing, but petty vengeance.\n"
"\n"
"<link=\"textShaky\">What is your identity?</link>\n"
"\n"
"Nothing, but a name spoken in disgust.\n"
"\n"
"<link=\"textShaky\">What do you want?</link>\n"
"\n"
"Nothing, but a new purpose.\n"
"\n"
"<link=\"textShaky\">What do you need?</link>\n"
"\n"
"Nothing, but the weapons that I trust.\n"
"\n"
"<link=\"textShaky\">So, where will you go?</link>\n"
"\n"
"Wherever you make me go.\n"
"\n"
"<link=\"textShaky\">Then, what will you do?</link>\n"
"\n"
"Whatever you say you need.\n"
"\n"
"<link=\"textShaky\">Is that all, then?</link>\n"
"\n"
"If you say it so.\n"
"\n"
"<link=\"textShaky\">Then go there, and die.</link>\n"
"\n"
"...\n"
"\n"
"As long as you're paying me.\n"
"\n"
msgstr ""

