#: .uk.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFDUALITY_NAME
msgid "Relic of Duality"
msgstr "Реліквія дуальності"

#: .uk.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFDUALITY_DESC
msgid ""
"Damaging enemies burns them for <style=cMono>FIGURE OUT THIS MATH LOL</style> "
"<style=cStack>(+something% per stack)</style>. <style=cDeath>Being hit "
"freezes you for some seconds idfk lol figure out when this item is "
"implemented</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFDUALITY_PICKUP
msgid "All attacks burn enemies. <style=cDeath>All damage freezes you.</style>"
msgstr ""
"Всі атаки підпалюють ворогів. <style=cDeath>Вся шкода заморожує вас.</style>"

#: .uk.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFDUALITY_LORE
msgid ""
"Hmm? Oh, Youngling! You are back sooner than expected. Have you completed "
"your search?\n"
"\n"
"Oh, dear. Youngling, why are you shivering? Has something hurt you?\n"
"\n"
"You found something that hurt you? Hmm. Peculiar. Do you have it with you, "
"still?\n"
"\n"
"...I see. Let me look at it, then. Come now, and show me what you've found.\n"
"\n"
"Hmm. A strange thing, this one. A blazing fire, yet cold to the touch. How "
"unnatural, this is. There's a certain harmony to it, however. As the heat "
"brings warmth and life, the cold tempers it, and keeps it in check. But in "
"that same way, that bitter cold may bring despair and death without the heat "
"to stave it off.\n"
"\n"
"...Oh, but there I go, rambling once more. You need to be taken care of, "
"Youngling. Please, come with me."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFEXTINCTION_NAME
msgid "Relic of Extinction"
msgstr "Реліквія вимирання"

#: .uk.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFEXTINCTION_DESC
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFEXTINCTION_DESC"
msgid "WIP DESC"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_ITEM_RELICOFEXTINCTION_PICKUP
