#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_NAME
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_NAME"
msgid "Executioner"
msgstr "Кат"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_SUBTITLE
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_SUBTITLE"
msgid "Dreaded Guillotine"
msgstr "Жахаюча гільйотина"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"The Executioner's goal is to spill as much blood as possible in the shortest "
"amount of time. Bullets loaded, ion manipulators charged.\n"
"\n"
"<color=#CCD3E0> < ! > Use Service Pistol to score kills to charge your Ion "
"Manipulators - or charge them manually during downtime.\n"
"\n"
"< ! > Ion Burst is at its strongest when used at maximum charge. Spread its "
"shots across a crowd to maximize its shocking effect.\n"
"\n"
"< ! > Execution is a great crowd control AND single target tool. Don't forget "
"that its damage depends on how many targets it hits!\n"
"\n"
"< ! > Use Crowd Dispersion to manipulate enemies and set them up for a well-"
"placed Execution."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_OUTRO_FLAVOR
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_OUTRO_FLAVOR"
msgid "..and so he left, an empty shell of armor drenched in blood."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_OUTRO_FAILURE
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_OUTRO_FAILURE"
msgid "..and so he vanished, escaping the inevitable."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_LORE
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_LORE"
msgid ""
"Death is inevitable. It comes for us all. Some may try to evade it, or run "
"from it. But death arrives all the same. Death, however, is simply the cost "
"of war. And death in glorious combat is one of the best deaths a man could "
"ask for.\n"
"\n"
"But, as always, some would seek to run from death. We call them by many "
"names. Deserters, cowards, turncoats. Each and every one of them, traitors to "
"the cause. These traitors must be punished for their crime. And that "
"punishment: in an ironic twist, is the very thing they tried to avoid.\n"
"\n"
"Death will come for them. Not as a robed spectre with a scythe. Not in a "
"trench coat, holding a revolver. Not as a sickness, nor the wear of time. No. "
"For them, death will come bearing lustrous battlegarb, with service pistol "
"loaded, and ion manipulators fully charged."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_KEYWORD_FEAR2
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName>Fear</style><style=cSub>Causes afflicted enemies to stop "
"attacking and flee. Enemies are slowed by 50%, and executed at 15% health or "
"below.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_KEYWORD_EXECUTING2
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName>Executing</style><style=cSub>Damage and proc coefficient "
"are doubled if no more than one enemy is hit. Kills double gained Ion "
"Manipulator stocks.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_KEYWORD_RECHARGING2
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName>Recharging</style><style=cSub>This skill can recharge "
"additional stocks by holding the button or killing enemies. Additional stocks "
"increase maximum capacity.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_KEYWORD_IONARMORBUFF
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName>Ion Armor</style><style=cSub>Increases armor by 60 and "
"decreases skill cooldowns by 20%.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_SKIN_EXECUTIONER2_DEFAULT
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_SKIN_EXECUTIONER2_DEFAULT"
msgid "Default"
msgstr "Стандартний"

#: .uk.SS2_SKIN_EXECUTIONER2_MASTERY
