msgstr "Воїн"

#: .uk.SS2_SKIN_EXECUTIONER2_ELECTRO
msgid "Electrocutioner"
msgstr "Електрокат"

#: .uk.SS2_SKIN_EXECUTIONER2_CLASSIC
msgid "Nostalgic"
msgstr "Ностальгійний"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_PISTOL_NAME
msgid "Service Pistol"
msgstr "Службовий пістолет"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_PISTOL_DESCRIPTION
msgid "Fire your pistol for <style=cIsDamage>180% damage</style>."
msgstr "Стріляє з пістолета, що завдає <style=cIsDamage>180% шкоди</style>."

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_EXECUTION_NAME
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_EXECUTION_NAME"
msgid "Execution"
msgstr "Страта"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_EXECUTION_DESC
msgid ""
"<style=cIsDamage>Executing</style>. Leap up, and <style=cIsDamage>slam</"
"style> down with an ion axe for <style=cIsDamage>1450% damage</style>. "
"<style=cIsUtility>Hold to aim.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_FIRINGSQUAD_NAME
msgid "Fusillade"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_FIRINGSQUAD_DESC
msgid ""
"<style=cIsDamage>Shocking</style>. Summon a firing squad of ion guns, rapidly "
"firing ion bullets for <style=cIsDamage>350% damage</style> per bullet but "
"losing <style=cIsHealth>-60% movement speed</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Hold "
"to extend duration. Cooldown scales with usage length.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_IONBURST_NAME
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_IONBURST_NAME"
msgid "Ion Burst"
msgstr "Іонна черга"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_IONBURST_DESC
msgid ""
"<style=cIsDamage>Shocking</style>. Rapidly discharge <style=cIsUtility>Ion "
"Manipulator stocks</style> as ion bullets for <style=cIsDamage>350% damage</"
"style> per bullet."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_IONCHARGE_NAME
msgid "Ion Manipulators"
msgstr "Іонний маніпулятор"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_IONCHARGE_DESC
msgid ""
"Hold to begin building up to <style=cIsUtility>10 stocks</style>, and replace "
"your <style=cIsDamage>primary skill</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Killing "
"enemies also adds stocks.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_DASH_NAME
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_DASH_NAME"
msgid "Crowd Dispersion"
msgstr "Дисперсія натовпу"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_DASH_DESC
msgid ""
"<style=cIsUtility>Dash</style> forward and inspire <style=cIsUtility>fear</"
"style> in nearby enemies.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_IONJUGGERNAUT_NAME
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_IONJUGGERNAUT_NAME"
msgid "Ion Overlord"
msgstr "Іонний повелитель"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER2_IONJUGGERNAUT_DESC
msgid ""
"Swing your ion axe for <style=cIsDamage>1700% damage</style> while held. "
"Activating begins slowly consuming <style=cIsUtility>Ion Manipulator charges</"
"style> to project ion armor."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_NAME
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_NAME"
msgid "Executioner"
msgstr "Кат"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_SUBTITLE
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_SUBTITLE"
msgid "Dreaded Guillotine"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"The Executioner is a high-risk, high-reward survivor that's all about racking "
"up an endless kill count.\n"
"\n"
"<color=#CCD3E0> < ! > Use Service Pistol to score some kills, with each kill "
"building up an even stronger Ion Burst.\n"
"\n"
"< ! > You can tap Ion Burst to fire a few shots, or hold it to fire them "
"all.\n"
"\n"
"< ! > Execution is a great crowd control AND single target tool. Don't forget "
"that its damage depends on how many targets it hits!\n"
"\n"
"< ! > If you find yourself getting swarmed, Crowd Dispersion can get enemies "
"off your back fast."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_OUTRO_FLAVOR
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_OUTRO_FLAVOR"
msgid "..and so he left, an empty shell of armor drenched in blood."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_OUTRO_FAILURE
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_OUTRO_FAILURE"
msgid "..and so he vanished, escaping the inevitable."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_LORE
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_LORE"
msgid ""
"Death is inevitable. It comes for us all. Some may try to evade it, or run "
"from it. But death arrives all the same. Death, however, is simply the cost "
"of war. And death in glorious combat is one of the best deaths a man could "
"ask for.\n"
"\n"
"But, as always, some would seek to run from death. We call them by many "
"names. Deserters, cowards, turncoats. Each and every one of them, traitors to "
"the cause. These traitors must be punished for their crime. And that "
"punishment: in an ironic twist, is the very thing they tried to avoid.\n"
"\n"
"Death will come for them. Not as a robed spectre with a scythe. Not in a "
"trench coat, holding a revolver. Not as a sickness, nor the wear of time. No. "
"For them, death will come bearing lustrous battlegarb, with service pistol "
"loaded, and ion manipulators fully charged."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_KEYWORD_FEAR
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName>Fear</style><style=cSub>Causes afflicted enemies to stop "
"attacking and flee. Enemies afflicted with fear take 50% more damage and have "
"their movement speed slowed by 30%.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_KEYWORD_EXECUTING
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName>Executing</style><style=cSub>Deals doubled damage if no "
"more than 1 enemy is hit.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_KEYWORD_RECHARGING
msgid ""
"<style=cKeywordName>Recharging</style><style=cSub>Killing enemies restores "
"charges of this skill, depending on the strength of the slain enemy. Doubled "
"charges with kills from Execution.</style>"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_PASSIVE_NAME
msgid "Bloodbath"
msgstr "Кривава баня"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_PASSIVE_DESC
msgid ""
"Killing enemies inflicted with <style=cIsUtility>fear</style> reduces all "
"skill cooldowns by <style=cIsUtility>1 second</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_TASER_NAME
msgid "Deadly Voltage"
msgstr "Смертельний вольтаж"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_TASER_DESCRIPTION
msgid "Fire arcs of lightning forward for <style=cIsDamage>{0}% damage</style>."
msgstr ""
"Випускає електричну дугу, що завдає <style=cIsDamage>{0}% шкоди</style>."

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_SWINGAXE_NAME
msgid "Ion Axe"
msgstr "Іонна сокира"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_SWINGAXE_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Swing your axe for <style=cIsDamage>% damage</style>. <style=cIsUtility>Each "
"Secondary charge grants 4% maximum health in shield</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_IONGUN_NAME
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_IONGUN_NAME"
msgid "Ion Burst"
msgstr "Іонна черга"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_IONGUN_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"<style=cIsUtility>Recharging.</style> Fire a barrage of ionized bullets, "
"dealing <style=cIsDamage>{0}% damage</style> each. <style=cIsUtility>Up to 5 "
"charges are fired at a time</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_IONBLAST_NAME
msgid "Ion Blast"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_IONBLAST_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Fire a blast of raw ion energy for <style=cIsDamage>% damage</style>. Can be "
"<style=cIsUtility>charged</style>, using multiple charges at once. "
"<style=cIsUtility>Restocks charges for every enemy you kill, depending on "
"strength</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_DASH_NAME
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_DASH_NAME"
msgid "Crowd Dispersion"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_DASH_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Boost forward and <style=cIsUtility>fear</style> all nearby enemies for "
