"<style=cIsUtility>Heavy</style>. <style=cIsDamage>Executing.</style> Launch "
"into the air and slam downwards with a massive ion axe for "
"<style=cIsDamage>{0}% damage</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_AXESCEPTER_NAME
msgid "Crowd Execution"
msgstr "Страта натовпу"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_AXESCEPTER_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Launch into the air and slam downward with your ion axe for "
"<style=cIsDamage>3000% damage</style>."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_ARMOR_NAME
msgid "Ion Juggernaut"
msgstr "Іонний джаґернаут"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_ARMOR_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Equip a suit of ionized armor, giving <style=cIsUtility>60 armor</style> and "
"<style=cIsDamage>supercharging</style> your secondary skill for "
"<style=cIsDamage>4</style> seconds."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_ARMORSCEPTER_NAME
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_ARMORSCEPTER_NAME"
msgid "Ion Overlord"
msgstr "Іонний повелитель"

#: .uk.SS2_EXECUTIONER_ARMORSCEPTER_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"Equip a suit of ionized armor, giving <style=cIsUtility>80 armor</style> and "
"<style=cIsDamage>supercharging</style> your secondary skill for "
"<style=cIsDamage>4</style> seconds. Killing enemies <style=cIsUtility>fears</"
"style> nearby enemies for 4 seconds."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_KNIGHT_BODY_NAME
msgid "Knight"
msgstr "Лицар"

#: .uk.SS2_KNIGHT_BODY_SUBTITLE
msgid "Royal Guard"
msgstr "Королівський гвардієць"

#: .uk.SS2_KNIGHT_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"The Knight is a skilled expert in melee combat, dueling and parrying foes "
"with precise timing and execution.\n"
"\n"
"<color=#CCD3E0>< ! > parry."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_KNIGHT_OUTRO_FLAVOR
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_KNIGHT_OUTRO_FLAVOR"
msgid "..and so he left, battered to the core of hope."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_KNIGHT_OUTRO_FAILURE
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_KNIGHT_OUTRO_FAILURE"
msgid "..and so he vanished, shield shattered and hope snuffed out."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_KNIGHT_BODY_LORE
msgid "why are there knights in space"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_KNIGHT_PASSIVE_NAME
msgid "Valor"
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_KNIGHT_PASSIVE_DESC
