#: .uk.SS2_NEMMANDO_SUBTITLE
msgctxt ".uk.SS2_NEMMANDO_SUBTITLE"
msgid "Lone Echo"
msgstr "Самотнє відлуння"

#: .uk.SS2_NEMMANDO_DESCRIPTION
msgid ""
"The Nemesis Commando is a wildcard on the battlefield, capable of turning any "
"situation to his favor.\n"
"\n"
"<color=#CCD3E0>< ! > Blade of Cessation is risky but can build up a lot of "
"damage by stacking Gouge.\n"
"\n"
"< ! > Distant Gash can be used to safely apply stacks of Gouge to groups of "
"enemies - take advantage of its piercing!\n"
"\n"
"< ! > Proper balance of melee and ranged combat is key, and Tactical Roll "
"grants high armor to help enter and exit battles.\n"
"\n"
"< ! > Submission can be utilized as huge burst of damage, whether it be to "
"aid in an escape or get the jump on an unsuspecting target."
msgstr ""

#: .uk.SS2_NEMMANDO_OUTRO_FLAVOR
